OL,3,CMan pictured confronting riot police
OL,4,Coutside asylum hotel jailed
OL,6,FA man who was pictured confronting
OL,7,Fpolice during a riot at a hotel
OL,8,Fhousing asylum seekers has been jailed.
OL,10,FHaulage business owner Ricky Hardman,
OL,11,F41, was photographed squaring up to
OL,12,Fofficers at the Holiday Inn Express in
OL,13,FManvers, Rotherham, on Sunday 4 August.
OL,15,FJailing him for two years and eight
OL,16,Fmonths, a judge told him he was part
OL,17,Fof an "ignorant mob".
