OL,3,CMan pictured confronting riot police
OL,4,Coutside asylum hotel jailed
OL,6,FTrouble flared after hundreds of
OL,7,Fpeople gathered outside the hotel in a
OL,8,Fseries of anti-immigration protests
OL,9,Fheld in the wake of the murders of
OL,10,Fthree girls in Southport.
OL,12,FPolice were attacked, the hotel's
OL,13,Fwindows were smashed and a bin was
OL,14,Fpushed against the building and set
OL,15,Falight during the incident.
OL,17,FHardman was arrested after a picture
OL,18,Fof him brandishing a piece of wood was
OL,19,Fpublished by the Daily Telegraph, a
OL,20,Fjudge was told on Monday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
