OL,3,CMan pictured confronting riot police
OL,4,Coutside asylum hotel jailed
OL,6,FVideo was played to Sheffield Crown
OL,7,FCourt showing him as part of a group
OL,8,Fattacking a police dog van during the
OL,9,Fviolence outside the hotel.
OL,11,FHardman, of Norfolk Road, Barnsley,
OL,12,Fcould be seen kicking out at the
OL,13,Fpolice van, which was being prevented
OL,14,Ffrom moving by people lying in front
OL,15,Fof it.
OL,17,FHe could then be seen as part of a
OL,18,Fgroup of about six men who violently
OL,19,Frocked the vehicle before it managed
OL,20,Fto drive away.
