OL,3,CMan pictured confronting riot police
OL,4,Coutside asylum hotel jailed
OL,6,FThe Recorder of Sheffield, Judge
OL,7,FJeremy Richardson KC, told Hardman the
OL,8,F"major civil disorder" was
OL,9,F"perpetrated by an ignorant mob of
OL,10,Fwhich you were a part".
OL,12,FHe went on: "The incident was part of
OL,13,Fwider national civic unrest fostered
OL,14,Fby some form of malignancy in society
OL,15,Fspread by malevolent users of social
OL,16,Fmedia.
OL,18,F"There's no question the disorder was
OL,19,Fracist in character and extremely
OL,20,Ffrightening for anyone who was there."
