OL,3,CMan pictured confronting riot police
OL,4,Coutside asylum hotel jailed
OL,6,FThe judge said he could not be sure
OL,7,Fthat Hardman threw the piece of wood
OL,8,Fhe was brandishing at the police but
OL,9,Fthought he "almost certainly" did.
OL,11,FHe said he was at the front of a mob
OL,12,Fattacking and threatening police, who
OL,13,Fwere "shamefully waving the Union
OL,14,Fflag".
OL,16,FThe judge said the police officers who
OL,17,Fprotected the hotel against the
OL,18,Frioters are "deserving of the highest
OL,19,Fpraise".
