OL,3,CMan pictured confronting riot police
OL,4,Coutside asylum hotel jailed
OL,6,FHe said: "It must be made clear that
OL,7,Fthose participating in this form of
OL,8,Fviolent disorder will be punished
OL,9,Fseverely by the courts.
OL,11,F"It is the duty of the court to do
OL,12,Fwhat it can to protect the public."
OL,14,FJudge Richardson said the maximum
OL,15,Fsentence for violent disorder was five
OL,16,Fyears in prison.
OL,18,FHe said there were others who were
OL,19,Ffacing sentencing for even more
OL,20,Fserious involvement in the Rotherham
OL,21,Fdisorder.
