OL,3,CMan pictured confronting riot police
OL,4,Coutside asylum hotel jailed
OL,6,FThe judge was told about a series of
OL,7,Fdefendants due to appear before him in
OL,8,Frelation to the Rotherham disorder in
OL,9,Fcoming days and how the efficiency
OL,10,Fwith which these cases is being dealt
OL,11,Fis leading to knock-on inefficiencies
OL,12,Fin relation to other prosecutions.
OL,14,FHe agreed, but said: "Major civil
OL,15,Fdisorder of this kind has to be
OL,16,Fprioritised."
OL,18,FRichard Davies, defending, told the
OL,19,Fjudge his client is "ashamed of
OL,20,Fhimself and the impact that it's going
OL,21,Fto have on his family".
