OL,3,CMan pictured confronting riot police
OL,4,Coutside asylum hotel jailed
OL,6,FHe said Hardman did not go to the
OL,7,Fhotel to get involved with violence
OL,8,Fbut got "carried away".
OL,10,FMr Davies said his client agrees that
OL,11,Fhe has "only got himself to blame".
OL,13,FHardman, of Norfolk Road, Barnsley,
OL,14,Fadmitted violent disorder last week.
OL,16,FHe sat in the dock with one security
OL,17,Fguard, wearing a black T-shirt and
OL,18,Fgreen trousers, and with his family
OL,19,Fwatching from the public gallery.
